<p>Many eggs in the workplace indicate a promotion soon, and he will be able to achieve all of his professional goals.  As for anyone planning something new, many eggs in a dream are a sign that he will achieve this thing.</p>
<p>The interpretation of the dream in the merchant's dream symbolizes the expansion of his trade and the achievement of profits that he has not achieved before, for many eggs indicate the end of competition in the life of the state and an improvement in his relationship with everyone around him.</p>
