<p>Many eggs in a dream for a married woman indicate that she will achieve many financial gains in the coming period, but if the husband is planning to enter into a new project, then the dream warns of its success and achieving many <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-البيض-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3554" > vision of eggs </a> boiled.  in the dream is evidence of achieving the desired goals with the ability to face the obstacles that appear along the way.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
