<p>The interpretation of a dream of gathering many eggs in a dream for a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> symbolizes the good work she does and always brings her closer to Almighty God.  It expresses poor health.</p>
