<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الجار-في-المنام?page=3071" > Seeing the neighbor </a> in a dream means an increase in friendship and relationships from relatives and other concepts, and we will refer to the unmarried girl, to the pregnant married woman, such as talking to the neighbors, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-بنات-الجيران-في-المنام?page=2417" > seeing the daughters of the neighbors </a> , entering the neighbor's house or seeing the neighbor's son in <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and others.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of neighbors in a dream</span></h2>
<p>If you <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الجيران-في-المنام?page=922" > see the neighbors </a> in a dream, it indicates that the dreamer is expecting something and therefore feels very stressed on his nerves, and this vision also shows that some people are talking and gossiping about the dreamer and this will negatively affect them all.  Relationships may deteriorate for a while.</p>
<p>The presence of neighbors in a dream means that some people will interfere in family life and this will lead to many problems.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
