<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الجيران-في-المنام?page=922" > Seeing the neighbors </a> in a dream means that the dreamer prefers not to share the details of his life with those around him, he is a good person at hiding his secrets and staying away from everyone.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الجار-في-المنام?page=3071" > Seeing the neighbor </a> in a dream, these visions can be interpreted for good or bad.  As for seeing a dear neighbor with insight, this means achieving good and happy events, but when you see a neighbor who quarrels with him in reality, this means his misfortune, and he goes through sad days and situations.</p>
<p>If you saw your neighbor in a dream, it means that you will hear very good news in a short time.  insight and this will make him very sad.<br/>And when you meet one of the neighbors with a smiling face in a dream, this indicates achieving abundance in nourishment and mercy.<br/>And when he meets an angry neighbor in a dream, this indicates the occurrence of some bad events and situations.<br/>As for the neighbors who return home in a dream, this indicates awareness of good and happy news.<br/>And take food or drink from the neighbor through the squares of good fortune and goodness.</p>
<p>Declares <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/مترجم-الأحلام-محمد-بن-سيرين?page=3415" > dream translator Muhammad ibn Sirin </a> that his vision does not bode well, as it indicates an increase in the dreamer's enemies and their strength, and therefore the dreamer will look for ways in which he can resist them.  Efforts will be greatly increased to overcome these situations and eliminate them.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
