</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In general, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الجيران-في-المنام?page=922" > seeing neighbors </a> in a dream symbolizes a woman's friends and relatives.<br/>Watching neighbors meet in a dream means happiness and happiness for the woman in reality.<br/>If the dreamer sees herself arguing with her neighbor, the dream shows her arrogance and the dreamer's vanity.<br/>- And if a woman sees in her dream that her neighbor is talking about her in her absence, this is evidence that the latter is doing so in reality.<br/>Giving a woman a gift to her neighbor in a dream means <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-الصداقة-والحب-في-المنام?page=1837" > friendship and love </a> between them.<br/>The woman who watches her neighbors in her sleep spying on her warns that she is veiled and people talk about her behind her back in reality.<br/>The woman who sees her neighbor with her husband in a dream is evidence of her lack of trust in people in reality.<br/>Seeing a woman's joy in her neighbor's house is an indication of her happiness in reality.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of neighbors in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>It has been mentioned in the interpretations of dreams that entering the neighbor's house after his permission and settling in it is an indication of the good that the newcomer offers to his neighbor, if the newcomer is from among the righteous, the people of piety and devout worshipers who fear God Almighty in prosperity and adversity.<br/>It was also said: This may be a statement that whoever entered the house received grace from its owner, such as helping him with a sum of money, or assisting him in building something.</p>
<p>And it happened that if someone knocked on his neighbor's door and the neighbor opened the door, welcoming him with a happy and cheerful face, drawing on him the marks of joy and delight, then this indicates that the visitor is receiving good from him.  his neighbor.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
