	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>It was said to Sheikh Muhammad ibn Shireen: Whoever sees in a dream that he is absent from his neighbor's house without his permission, this indicates that he revealed his neighbor's secret and made him aware of what he hides from people, and there he knows the hidden things in the secret of that neighbor that no one knows except God.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of entering the neighbor's house in a dream</span></h2>
<p>A person's entry into his neighbor's house in a dream may indicate betrayal that befalls him and targeting him, and this may include betrayal of the neighbor's wife and her honor, or betrayal in other matters of life.  This will be a sign of the envy buried in the heart of the one who returned home, jealous of his neighbor for all the blessings, righteous deeds, and pleasure in this world that he has.</p>
<p>It was also said: If he is seen entering his neighbor's house after he has asked for his permission and responded to him, and the beginner was from the sinners, this indicates that the visitor shared in his neighbor's evil deed and committed sin.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
