</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of knocking on the neighbors' door in a dream</span></h2>
<p>It has also been mentioned that if someone knocks on his neighbor's door and no one answers him, this means that the person will not achieve what he desires, and it may also mean that the fortune-teller angered his neighbor with him, so he did not do so.  He answered and did not open the door for him.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the neighbor entering the house in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The neighbor who enters the dreamer's house and sits with him at the table in a dream is a praiseworthy vision that bodes well for the dreamer and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-كسب-المال-في-المنام?page=3081" > earning money </a>.<br/>A neighbor's visit to the deity with the intention of marrying one of his daughters means that the dreamer will hear good news in the near future.<br/>The entry of a sick neighbor into the dreamer's house portends that in reality there will be a misunderstanding between them.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a neighbor entering a dream without permission</span></h2>
<p>Whoever sees in a dream that he entered his neighbor's house without permission, then he enters his neighbor's secret or knows his neighbor's secret that he hides from people, but if he sees this wicked person betraying his neighbor to his wife.  He may commit adultery with his neighbor's wife, or steal from his house, or slow down to see her magic, or watch their life with envy.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
